column5: If you will be at the All Canada Show at Pheasant Run in St Charles Illinois on 1/15/12 stop by the Birch Dale Lodge Booth and introduce yourself. I'd like to meet you and be able to put a name with a face. Thanks, Terry
Terry, I'm close by and hope to meet you there.
i will also be there. check out the new ontario booth.

Iwas told that several people stopped by looking for me on Saturday, but due to work issues I wasn't able to get to the show until late that afternoon. I'm sorry I missed you. I was able to meet Duflebag on Sunday. It turned out to be a very good show in spite of the weather and NFL games.

Narda Stopped by Birch Dale Lodge booth Saturday to meet you and was told you had gone to the liquor store to purchase a bottle of Rye. Was that true? Anyway, sorry I missed you. Hope to see you next year! Marv
Someone was telling stories, I got there at about 4pm and I brought the rye with me!!
If I would have known you had it with you, I would have waited!!
You should have stuck around and had a few. Sorry I missed you.
